{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/steam_title_-_en.png?t=1731678823\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A game where the power of stories shapes reality, driven by AI language model...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adapted from Persian folklore: The brutal King Shahryar, enraged by suspected betrayal of his wife, takes a new bride each day only to execute her at dawn. You are Shahrzad, his next bride... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you end his reign of terror through your stories? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/spin_a_tale.png?t=1731678823\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/story.gif?t=1731678823\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Inspired by Wittgenstein's notion: &quot;The limits of my language mean the limits of my world.&quot;</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unleash your imagination!</strong> Tell captivating tales to intrigue the AI-powered King, cleverly guiding him to mention words like 'sword', 'knife', or 'shield' - watch as they materialize into real weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Brought to life by cutting-edge AI language models, each story is a unique creation - completely unscripted! But beware... strange words might provoke the King's wrath...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/turn_language_to_blade.png?t=1731678823\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/weapon.gif?t=1731678823\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Collect weapons forged from your stories! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Generated in real-time based on your narratives! From shawarma kitchen knives to witch's spears... every weapon is one of a kind!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/fight_with_king.png?t=1731678823\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/battle.gif?t=1731678823\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Battle the King in a world born from your tales! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each battle is an unprecedented theatrical performance - weapon effects and even character dialogues spring from the stories you've crafted!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>AI-Native Game: </strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Powered by generative AI (especially large language models) as core gameplay mechanics. In other words, this innovative experience would be impossible without AI. Award-winning gameplay ensures every story is unique!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pixel Art Aesthetics:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features distinctive pixel art and hand-drawn CGs! <i>AI is used solely for the innovative storytelling gameplay - all artwork is created by human artists.</i> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Challenge Traditional Norms: </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Break free from ancient patriarchal constraints with Shahrzad!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Academic Foundation:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More than just a game - it's an academic and artistic project. We've published two papers on the game's systems, hoping to inspire more novel games!</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Lady of the Sun","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2782660/3306fa28e74588b49d43e560b790ff075ae28423.jpg"},{"name":"Open Sesame!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2782660/60beb4cecab0566f7e118b1e50be37e2650601f7.jpg"},{"name":"First Blood","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2782660/24174042d0ce19e82ca25ba5e4c98942606899b3.jpg"},{"name":"Genesis!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2782660/094c2ecd6efc14a15bc301ce35980825783ce547.jpg"},{"name":"Bedtime Tale","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2782660/7c1554280d70bd796d4f59979383d1c6eda716fe.jpg"},{"name":"Nightfall","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2782660/24174042d0ce19e82ca25ba5e4c98942606899b3.jpg"},{"name":"The King's Rage!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2782660/cea3d07908bb446eb8bcd7d3a9de3672e1eaf8ce.jpg"},{"name":"Perilous Monarch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2782660/b16cf58ce64d1f50de5d72d993f0a6c047894f7c.jpg"},{"name":"Endless Night","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2782660/51740f6fd7af3cdb2294b373893158f39b3c1550.jpg"},{"name":"Grandmaster of Weapons","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2782660/0c58de6f64a387c876631c66a00fdef8b8528228.jpg"}],"total":12},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731678823","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1731678823","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731678823","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731678823","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Find us!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/english_welcome.png?t=1731678823\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>X </strong>@AdaEden1001 |\u00a0<strong>Tiktok</strong> @@1001nights.ai</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join our <strong>Discord</strong> through the right sidebar!</p></p><br><h1>About the Demo</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/steam_title_-_en.png?t=1731678823\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A game where the power of stories shapes reality, driven by AI language model...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adapted from Persian folklore: The brutal King Shahryar, enraged by suspected betrayal of his wife, takes a new bride each day only to execute her at dawn. You are Shahrzad, his next bride... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you end his reign of terror through your stories? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/spin_a_tale.png?t=1731678823\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/story.gif?t=1731678823\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Inspired by Wittgenstein's notion: &quot;The limits of my language mean the limits of my world.&quot;</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unleash your imagination!</strong> Tell captivating tales to intrigue the AI-powered King, cleverly guiding him to mention words like 'sword', 'knife', or 'shield' - watch as they materialize into real weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Brought to life by cutting-edge AI language models, each story is a unique creation - completely unscripted! But beware... strange words might provoke the King's wrath...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/turn_language_to_blade.png?t=1731678823\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/weapon.gif?t=1731678823\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Collect weapons forged from your stories! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Generated in real-time based on your narratives! From shawarma kitchen knives to witch's spears... every weapon is one of a kind!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/fight_with_king.png?t=1731678823\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/extras/battle.gif?t=1731678823\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Battle the King in a world born from your tales! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each battle is an unprecedented theatrical performance - weapon effects and even character dialogues spring from the stories you've crafted!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>AI-Native Game: </strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Powered by generative AI (especially large language models) as core gameplay mechanics. In other words, this innovative experience would be impossible without AI. Award-winning gameplay ensures every story is unique!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pixel Art Aesthetics:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features distinctive pixel art and hand-drawn CGs! <i>AI is used solely for the innovative storytelling gameplay - all artwork is created by human artists.</i> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Challenge Traditional Norms: </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Break free from ancient patriarchal constraints with Shahrzad!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Academic Foundation:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More than just a game - it's an academic and artistic project. We've published two papers on the game's systems, hoping to inspire more novel games!</p></li></ul>","developers":["Ada Eden"],"fullgame":{"appid":"2542850","name":"1001 Nights"},"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782660/header.jpg?t=1731678823","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> macOS 10.12+<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel or AMD Dual Core at 2 GHz or better<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Intel Graphics 4400 or better<br></li><li><strong>Network:</strong> Broadband Internet connection<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 3 GB available space</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257067711,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257067711/movie480.mp4?t=1730978092","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257067711/movie_max.mp4?t=1730978092"},"name":"Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257067711/90168d064be888529a7c5818846387192a68f643/movi